reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 30, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great for organization and have a surprisingly large capacity
reviews.reviewText: These days of the week packing cubes are super useful. I purchased them for my 6 year old daughter for an upcoming trip to keep her suitcase organized and everything easy to find but can see these being useful for a variety of other things like summer camp or even daily assignments or reading (if the books are small).Here's what to know about these cubes:-This comes with 2 sets, so you have two of each day of the week which would be perfect for sleepaway camp or a longer trip.-Each day is a different color, so it's easy to tell them apart in your suitcase.-These easily fit an entire outfit (including panties, socks and a bow) for my daughter. She's a size 6 and I definitely had more room in each cube. I was packing stretch pants and t-shirts but I think there would still be room for a sweatshirt or some heavier clothes.-I also tried out some of my clothes to see if I could use these. I'm a ladies medium and was able to get an entire outfit of mine in a cube as well. I added a t-shirt and pants but don't think I'd have enough room for one of my sweaters. These really are intended for kids.-The zippers are strong and we didn't have any issues getting them zipped/unzipped.I really like these for organization at the price point. They're bright and fun and will definitely save us time getting ready each day of our trip.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I FINALLY have a way to organize when I go away for week long trips!!These packing cubes are VERY spacious (and not as rigid as I thought they’d be), vibrant, and beautiful. The colors make me happy because I travel a lot to tropical destinations and these fit the vibes perfectly.A great value, as well!What I do specifically is I put my makeup, accessories, and clothes for that day in the cube (of course my makeup is wrapped and stuff before I just throw it on in there, same for my jewelry) but it REALLY does help when you’re on a trip and want a specific outfit for a specific day, etc. Worth the buy if you ask me!
